Elliott May Get National Express Cosmen Vote, Sky Says

-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 
2011-04-12T08:50:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/elliott-may-get-national-express-cosmen-vote-sky-says-correct-.html

  (Corrects attribution to the statement in first paragraph.)  Elliott Advisors U.K. Ltd., the
activist shareholder in  National Express Group Plc (NEX) , will
announce today that Spain’s Cosmen family will vote in support
of several resolutions proposed by Elliott for the company’s
annual meeting next month, Sky News editor Mark Kleinman
reported, citing a copy of a statement prepared by Elliott.   Elliott expects that the Cosmen family and its nominees
will back Elliott’s candidates for three new directors to the
board of  National Express , Kleinman said on his blog, citing the
statement.    To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Maria Ermakova at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net  